          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              One thing to note about the sub-$500 machines is that they use pressurized portafilters. This helps mask mistakes that the user makes, but also puts a pretty low ceiling on the quality of espresso you can make.

              

              
              
