              It was hard for me to relinquish control from my Gaggia of grinding, tamping, etc.  However with newborn twins and a 3-year old jr. barista (baristette?) I, for one, welcome my new espresso overlord:<br /><br /><div style="padding: 3px;">
  <div style="margin-bottom: 3px; font-weight: bold;" onclick="var q = $(this).parent().find('.quotecontent > div');q.toggle();$(this).find('span').html(q.is(':visible')?'hide':'show');return false;">
    <b>Spoiler: </b>
    <span style="color: #FF5B00; cursor: pointer;">show</span>
  </div>
