</div><br /><br />Never thought I could love a superautomatic; seemed to lack that artistic, human requirement.  But to be able to go from power-off to perfect, consistent (adjustable!) shot in about 2 minutes .. well .. it's the right setup for me at this stage of life  <img src="//cdn.arstechnica.net/civis/images/smilies/big_grin_classic.png" alt=":bigdumbgrin:" title="Big Grin" />

              

              
              
